data.description: Irresistible  A -13 Model Home Near Fairway Rec Center In Sun City. ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 5.25% (restrictions apply) plus an OWNED SOLAR SYSTEM, that Means No Monthly Solar Payments and low power bills. 2 Bedrooms 1.75 Bathrooms. The Guest Bathroom Has A Jetted Tub To Relax. The Kitchen Has Been Updated And Reconfigured, With Granite Countertops, A Bar To Eat At Or Desk Area, And Cabinets. The Arizona Room Has Been Added For More Livable Square Footage And Could Be Used As A Craft Area, Which The Current Owner Is Doing, Or A Family Room.  There Is A Courtyard In the Front Great For Enjoying Coffee Or Happy Hour. The Back Has A Covered Patio Overlooking Green Space. Please Stop By And See This Home Soon.
